# custom.txt.example — copy this file to custom.txt to get started:
#   cp allowlist-proxy-domains.d/custom.txt.example allowlist-proxy-domains.d/custom.txt
#
# custom.txt is gitignored so your internal patterns stay out of version control.
# Used by the self-healing daemon to reactively allow IPs whose resolved domain
# matches a pattern here. Format: *.example.com
#
# Examples:
#   *.your-cdn.example.com
